    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><h3 id="启动Elasticsearch集群前准备"><a href="#启动Elasticsearch集群前准备" class="headerlink" title="启动Elasticsearch集群前准备"></a>启动Elasticsearch集群前准备</h3><h4 id="创建用户及用户组"><a href="#创建用户及用户组" class="headerlink" title="创建用户及用户组"></a>创建用户及用户组</h4><p>Elasticsearch不能以root启动，因此需要添加非root用户:</p><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">groupadd es</span><br><span class="line">useradd es -g es</span><br><span class="line">chown -R es:es ./elasticsearch-6.4.2</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>为非root用户添加登陆密码：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">passwd es</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>我这里创建好后查看上菜单栏System–&gt;Administration–&gt;Users and Groups的结果如下：</p><p><img src="/article/2.JPG" alt=""></p><p><img src="/article/3.JPG" alt=""></p><p>开机的登录用户时可切换es用户</p><p><img src="/article/4.JPG" alt=""></p><h4 id="关闭防火墙"><a href="#关闭防火墙" class="headerlink" title="关闭防火墙"></a>关闭防火墙</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service iptables stop</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>以上命令适用于CentOS 6</p><p>CentOS 7 版本及以上使用命令如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl stop firewalld</span><br><span class="line">systemctl disable firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>至此，两个节点之间通信的前提条件准备好了</p><h3 id="启动Elasticsearch集群"><a href="#启动Elasticsearch集群" class="headerlink" title="启动Elasticsearch集群"></a>启动Elasticsearch集群</h3><h4 id="切换至es用户"><a href="#切换至es用户" class="headerlink" title="切换至es用户"></a>切换至es用户</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">su es</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h4 id="在两个节点上分别启动es服务"><a href="#在两个节点上分别启动es服务" class="headerlink" title="在两个节点上分别启动es服务"></a>在两个节点上分别启动es服务</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd bin</span><br><span class="line">./elasticsearch -d # 设置后台启动</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h4 id="访问浏览且查看启动效果："><a href="#访问浏览且查看启动效果：" class="headerlink" title="访问浏览且查看启动效果："></a>访问浏览且查看启动效果：</h4><p>节点1启动效果如下图所示：<br><img src="/article/5.JPG" alt=""></p><p>节点2启动效果如下图所示：<br><img src="/article/6.JPG" alt=""></p><h4 id="命令行查看集群信息："><a href="#命令行查看集群信息：" class="headerlink" title="命令行查看集群信息："></a>命令行查看集群信息：</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl http://127.0.0.1:9200/_cat/allocation?v</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>结果如下：<br><img src="/article/7.JPG" alt=""></p><h4 id="postman上插入数据"><a href="#postman上插入数据" class="headerlink" title="postman上插入数据"></a>postman上插入数据</h4><p><img src="/article/8.JPG" alt=""></p><p>curl查看数据入库结果如下图所示：<br><img src="/article/9.JPG" alt=""></p><h4 id="Other"><a href="#Other" class="headerlink" title="Other:"></a>Other:</h4><p>查看集群信息目录命令：<br><img src="/article/10.JPG" alt=""></p><h3 id="References"><a href="#References" class="headerlink" title="References:"></a>References:</h3><p>1.<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/genghaihua/article/details/81479619" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/genghaihua/article/details/81479619</a></p></body></html>]]></content>
    
